Package: indi-pentax
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libindi1, libpktriggercord, libricohcamerasdk [!arm64]
Description: INDI Pentax driver.
 Driver for Pentax DSLR cameras.
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.
 
Package: indi-pentax-dbg
Priority: extra
Section: debug
Architecture: any
Depends: indi-pentax (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: INDI Pentax driver.
 Driver for Pentax DSLR cameras.
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.
 This package contains the debug symbols for the this driver, useful to investigate problems in INDI.
